{"tid":406694,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"(港航/快運又有 mega sale)  海航疑連環押股籌錢","createTime":"2017-09-20T00:35:55.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-20T13:20:10.000Z","uid":6604,"like":12,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"2d9b45db3b154abc9476a26b16b83fcb9523cbf3","tid":406694,"uid":6604,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-20T00:35:55.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/financeestate/art/20170920/20158625\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Ffinanceestate%2Fart%2F20170920%2F20158625&d=AOcXI6WYhJzavXyt1VaMM8n%2FdpYTMnF8ODxps2tmzCA%3D&h=f058e6c1\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Ffinanceestate%2Fart%2F20170920%2F20158625&h=421e5caf\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/financeestate/art/20170920/20158625</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】海航集團一邊否認啟德地遭銀行退出再融資，但另一邊廂則連環押股籌錢。據聯交所資料披露，華融資產管理以「持有股份保證權益」，申報在9月12日（上周二）持有海航系的嘉耀控股（1626）、KTL（442）的控股權，分別為65.2%及74.96%股權，股權數目與海航所持股數相同，意味海航或向華融押盡持股。  <br />\n<br />\n料不足10億元<br />\n<br />\n按上周二收市價計，嘉耀及KTL兩股市值分別只有5.79億元及8.28億元，以海航持股量計算，佔兩公司市值分別只有3.78億及6.2億元，合共不足10億元，相對其35億元過渡貸款，以及項目的建築貸款貸款，再融資資金明顯不夠用。<br />\n海航去年在本港股市連環收購多間上市公司控股權，目前旗下已最少有8間本港上市公司在手，除了嘉耀及KTL，還有海航科技投資（2086，前稱龍傑智能卡）、香港建投（687）、航基股份（357）及海航實業（521）、東北電氣（042）、順客隆（974）等。<br />\n早前有報道指，海航啟德地的融資商討仍進行中，但未尋得牽頭行承擔大額融資，若最終再融資失敗，或導致海航資金斷鏈。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"35c480c1e20c532ea1e6195e2d08f3f0df46d5bd","tid":406694,"uid":35870,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-20T01:18:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"be0c617ccf60857e87b87f2b8c1a2f76c94d6946","tid":406694,"uid":6604,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-20T02:52:32.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n你買左 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d23d7992000895f1810b7aee9b2fe7edb6d4170a","tid":406694,"uid":51720,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-20T02:54:16.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n你買左 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n滿天翻車魚（拉丁文學名）<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncy.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"714f349c0816202b477a13e24aaee2bdb4f6be0c","tid":406694,"uid":26752,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-20T02:57:23.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9bcee74ed6a77ee199b79ce79e8b3a6cbbd30578","tid":406694,"uid":35870,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-20T03:08:44.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/no